[...]
slack   3666477 bgregg  mem     REG               7,16    141930     7165 /snap/slack/44/usr/lib/slack/chrome_100_percent.pak
slack   3666477 bgregg  mem     REG               7,16    165680     7433 /snap/slack/44/usr/lib/slack/v8_context_snapshot.bin
